text: Rob Summerfield is an American businessman and politician. Born in Bloomer, Wisconsin, Summerfield helped run his family business the Two Acres Supper Club. He also co-owned the Chippewa Valley Land Title Company. Summerfield has served in the Wisconsin State Assembly as a Republican since 2017.WisconsinVote.org.-Rob SummerfieldOurCandidate.com.-Rob Summerfield ==Notes== Category:Living people Category:People from Bloomer, Wisconsin Category:Businesspeople from Wisconsin Category:Wisconsin Republicans Category:Members of the Wisconsin State Assembly Category:1980 births
